{"tid":278701,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"親戚去左旅行 任命我為鏟屎官","createTime":"2017-06-10T16:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T08:31:56.000Z","uid":80386,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20469cbc3eacac8aced039563984287fb296a31d","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"可以做4日3夜鏟屎官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1f613494f25d68514287d5a8d2723eeb3a825e","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/000110_7ba0db56398cb3c8ea4390acd693f415.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F000110_7ba0db56398cb3c8ea4390acd693f415.jpg&h=2526394b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHello<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37acb718ebc853f920e3a460be64f118c83a6ba9","tid":278701,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cf64fed79a509f27dbfb14035968d22ca10e86","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:03:33.000Z","msg":"陣左比主子大家欣賞下 主要想同大家推介呢隻貓沙<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/000156_59e171cc23384a6819a7f9ab5f84c7e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F000156_59e171cc23384a6819a7f9ab5f84c7e9.jpg&h=e314add2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前個親戚用開木沙 要每晚都換晒啲木沙 轉左呢隻之後 可以每2-3晚先換一次 而且無咁大陣尿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e114c06d9b7fe3b06931b30bc6ac0a11cea7f17","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">除</span>左比主子大家欣賞下 主要想同大家推介呢隻貓沙</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3e91dc2a4648b0439dae20fd4ab548aecaf0b86a","tid":278701,"uid":104905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陣左比主子大家欣賞下 主要想同大家推介呢隻貓沙<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/000156_59e171cc23384a6819a7f9ab5f84c7e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F000156_59e171cc23384a6819a7f9ab5f84c7e9.jpg&h=e314add2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前個親戚用開木沙 要每晚都換晒啲木沙 轉左呢隻之後 可以每2-3晚先換一次 而且無咁大陣尿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用水晶砂無問題，小心隻攞嚟食"},{"pid":"9a0d344e96481eab05460df136741ec86883d1b2","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>陣左比主子大家欣賞下 主要想同大家推介呢隻貓沙<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/000156_59e171cc23384a6819a7f9ab5f84c7e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F000156_59e171cc23384a6819a7f9ab5f84c7e9.jpg&h=e314add2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前個親戚用開木沙 要每晚都換晒啲木沙 轉左呢隻之後 可以每2-3晚先換一次 而且無咁大陣尿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用水晶砂無問題，小心隻攞嚟食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用左一段時間都無問題 見佢痾完臭臭踢幾下就會出番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97cabc4f63f19cc917c3738651d4268d2e4aed13","tid":278701,"uid":104905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />砂可以厚多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9166fe6298206e283913d40fecd077a733f43e60","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />砂可以厚多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無話有咩唔好?<br />\n以前用木砂果陣多一倍 唔知點解而家用咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b45cbd5f3042dbebdc1b2adf71a5dc59cbb7a8","tid":278701,"uid":93402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以影個包裝睇下 🙈🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"929a00a4b97f010d2ae6ced0f0de73024e9b220c","tid":278701,"uid":104905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:15:37.000Z","msg":"大約5-8厘米厚的貓砂，貓會用得舒服啲，一日清兩次就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2922427608989d9786f9031422eced3f94066f60","tid":278701,"uid":104905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"用水晶砂個底唔使放紙吸尿(木砂先要)，就咁放砂就ok"},{"pid":"61a17fda95a8f594a9eab028f345d4f0665c1d0d","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主可唔可以影個包裝睇下 🙈🙏🏻🙏🏻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/013117_e88e88349ca9bd465c8238f25b92fbea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F013117_e88e88349ca9bd465c8238f25b92fbea.jpg&h=167ce9d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺廁所見到呢包 我位親戚好慳家 佢地用得嘅應該唔會貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363e04ef04532493141ee9d3699b978c7d9ccc5b","tid":278701,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"劉明"},{"pid":"4391c2683e43cc9df89e2c0f5e646a5a3c12732f","tid":278701,"uid":51758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:34:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3b8dc4005bce8cfef19c93242b57b2e8b2f48b0","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用水晶砂個底唔使放紙吸尿(木砂先要)，就咁放砂就ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要方便清潔 等啲砂唔會攝住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5ae78dc265cd543b43b956622588fa7cb9808b","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水晶砂唔吉腳仔咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該無 見佢痾得好暢快 痾完仲會堆砂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d906b9580e5a3eb0db6ddbefc29ef13123c74c52","tid":278701,"uid":104905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T22:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主可唔可以影個包裝睇下 🙈🙏🏻🙏🏻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/013117_e88e88349ca9bd465c8238f25b92fbea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F013117_e88e88349ca9bd465c8238f25b92fbea.jpg&h=167ce9d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺廁所見到呢包 我位親戚好慳家 佢地用得嘅應該唔會貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n$35包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e592a38410047510b2b63cb449c82bae6cf183","tid":278701,"uid":24529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T23:03:17.000Z","msg":"黎緊我成家都去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好唔放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f518352299b32d27b30ea22bc79d58ab0250078","tid":278701,"uid":12471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:05:33.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係用呢隻 堅吸味<br />\n不過嚟緊諗住換豆腐砂<br />\n利申 琴日開始做貓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a6be8f623541f3da8775994ecd1e5d04c85358","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T03:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊我成家都去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好唔放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無搵人照顧?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499acfa2fc5b139c4bda9806d2e2c9ee6a4517fc","tid":278701,"uid":105598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企都係用呢隻 堅吸味<br />\n不過嚟緊諗住換豆腐砂<br />\n利申 琴日開始做貓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n豆腐砂好流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我遇果隻唔好<br />\nD豆味溝屎尿味臭到仆街<br />\n又成日痴住主人"},{"pid":"5baf679e09b9a30e83001faa1690d334c1758dd7","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T03:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企都係用呢隻 堅吸味<br />\n不過嚟緊諗住換豆腐砂<br />\n利申 琴日開始做貓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未用過豆腐砂 不過應該都要成日換?<br />\n頭先上網睇一睇 原來好多人1-4星期先換一次 見到已經覺得臭 以前用木砂果陣 2日唔換 主子已經唔肯去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d308fdd65cad754969429de7327bb1ba6361f80a","tid":278701,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"用緊花王木砂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6154ea67cc868b798dd6c70dfce3b442eff7a77","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"一起身主子就同我玩伏匿匿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/123702_bc35474766241c8b45c67a8207ff2d5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F123702_bc35474766241c8b45c67a8207ff2d5a.jpg&h=917fd156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵左佢大半粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵完仲要唔理奴才<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8725bc763eaa00c76aab2538961e051d6ff8fc7","tid":278701,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0229f7212ba1328edab68166c66563658f9b6ac3","tid":278701,"uid":12471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我屋企都係用呢隻 堅吸味<br />\n不過嚟緊諗住換豆腐砂<br />\n利申 琴日開始做貓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未用過豆腐砂 不過應該都要成日換?<br />\n頭先上網睇一睇 原來好多人1-4星期先換一次 見到已經覺得臭 以前用木砂果陣 2日唔換 主子已經唔肯去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主要係驚佢地細個會食<br />\n但係暫時都正常使用中"},{"pid":"49b4736e6ada406e55fabeac635f4c6e14b6e660","tid":278701,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:34:16.000Z","msg":"小二！我要圖！"},{"pid":"01985d68e7d19377d3e7e41c8ad2ceb1a6210a02","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩又搵左主子15分鐘 搵晒啲櫃唔都唔見佢 原去左扮公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/162005_0be1400ce88d914b5aff7faf3ff037f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F162005_0be1400ce88d914b5aff7faf3ff037f3.jpg&h=60e84e39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"956ef1bae25c9f1832b7d21498848f52482a8345","tid":278701,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30ce3dbec45b1fdbef3ac550d8d39e93ac080a19","tid":278701,"uid":80386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"比佢掃晒啲公仔落地 成地死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/162313_49ba29dce87ca45c6